profile_positions.description:
2ndHomes is a sales organization of International Real Estate in varying beautiful & special parts of the world. Special because of certain characteristics, environments, projects and by interesting capital gains and high R.O.I. of these areas. Mainly targeting new, upcoming areas or emerging markets, specializing in Bali, Brazil, Thailand, Cyprus, Ibiza, Panama and USA (a.o. Trump projects).
Exposure Project Development is a subsidiary of Exposure Enterprises. Its objective is to develop small scale (between 10 - 50 units) residential real estate projects in various parts of the world. These projects share a couple of pre-defined characteristics in common:
	Locations are in areas of outstanding natural beauty;
	We will only target countries that are being considered stable in terms of political climate and economic environment;
	The quality of the residential buildings meet without exception the demands of a very discerning clientele;
	The real estate developments have to create a warm atmosphere, making prospective buyers feel comfortable immediately;
	Making the transition for any client that wishes to relocate permanently an easy process;
	Find areas to develop with interesting tax conditions and high capital appreciations;

With the recent changing of the global economies and longer life expectancies for many developed countries a growing number of people are considering a new era in some of the more beautiful parts of the world. It is mainly this group that we try to offer a solution. But we also have a growing list of prospective buyers that consider acquiring real estate for holiday use or as a financial investment.
Part of our construction service is as well Flex-Building-Bali (Brazil + Thailand) for individual home construction with a variety of pre-designed models from us to chose from (so save architect costs) that we construct on chosen plots.:
